WEBVTT

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:34.080
before we can fully finance
all our conservation efforts.

00:14:35.280 --> 00:14:36.520
But neither Bhutan,

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:38.920
nor the world

00:14:39.480 --> 00:14:42.640
can afford to spend 15 years
going backwards.

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:46.840
This is why His Majesty the King

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:49.360
started Bhutan For Life.

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.896
Bhutan For Life gives us the time we need.

00:14:52.920 --> 00:14:54.320
It gives us breathing room.

00:14:55.120 --> 00:14:57.496
It is essentially a funding mechanism

00:14:57.520 --> 00:14:59.456
to look after our parks,

00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:00.920
to protect our parks,